  last commit cause _major_ access violations during emerge.  Reverting

  04 Jan 2004; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> qt-3.3.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Test for compile fix - let Qt write to some sysconf directories
  when emerging.

